title: Demon God of Apocalyptic Behemoth
description: Demon God of Apocalyptic Behemoth Manhua A bustling city and a peaceful society are instantly destroyed by a sudden apocalypse. Countless polluted monsters flood the world, forbidden zones appear, connecting doomsday worlds, leading to the death of billions and seas of blood. During this time, the silently growing Chen Chu, comparable to a god, steps forward.
